	skos:narrower <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/293> , <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/1100> , <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/1146> , <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/1329> , <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/1338> , <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/1736> , <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/1776> , <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/1810> , <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/324> , <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/35> , <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/628> , <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/675> , <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/686> , <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/786> , <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/97> , <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/2109> .

