	skos:definition "The axis of an ellipse that is perpendicular to the major axis at a point equidistant from the foci."@en .

<http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/1066> a rdfs:Resource , skos:Concept ;
	dcterms:modified "2020-12-16T15:43:34.765Z"^^xsd:dateTime ;
