	skos:definition "The mathematical problem of studying the behavior (e.g., velocities, positions) of any number of objects moving under their mutual gravitational attraction for any time in the past or future."@en .

<http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/211> a rdfs:Resource , skos:Concept ;
	dcterms:modified "2020-11-03T19:00:34.397Z"^^xsd:dateTime ;
	dcterms:contributor <http://editor.vocabs.ands.org.au/user/AAS_Frey.Katie> ;
	skos:broader <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/661> ;
