	skos:narrower <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/570> , <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/1312> , <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/568> , <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/569> .

<http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/1313> a rdfs:Resource , skos:Concept ;
	skos:broader <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/343> ;
	skos:prefLabel "Quantum cosmology"@en .

