	skos:prefLabel "Reionization"@en , "Reionisation"@en-gb ;
	skos:definition "The ionization of neutral hydrogen atoms formed during recombination epoch in the early Universe."@en .

<http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/223> a rdfs:Resource , skos:Concept ;
