	skos:related <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/2037> ;
	skos:scopeNote "Specific to interactions between the Sun and Earth.  The similar concept \"Solar-planetary interactions\" is about interactions between the Sun and other Solar system planets, or all of them more generally."@en .

<http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/1474> a rdfs:Resource , skos:Concept ;
