	skos:narrower <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/2045> , <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/221> , <http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/869> ;
	skos:definition "Collapse of a mass of material as a result of the mutual gravitational attraction of all its constituents."@en .

