	skos:definition "In the Galactic coordinate system, the angle between the line of sight to an object and the Galactic equator. Galactic latitude ranges from +90 degrees to -90 degrees."@en .

<http://astrothesaurus.org/uat/569> a rdfs:Resource , skos:Concept ;
